The paper describes a tool for visualization and analysis of multidimensional vectorial data, which involves machine learning and data analysis techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
